				<td colspan="2"><span>First thing you do is hie yourself back to shadeweavers and get an &quot;Ivory Horn&quot;.  It's a primary slot wind instrument.
<br />

<br />
I have found at 29 that things sort of depend on what (and where) I am fighting.  I have noticed that I can get and keep agro better if I am using an instrument in my twist than if I am not.  Other than than, unless I am doing something VERY, VERY wrong, it doesn't seem to make much difference.
<br />

<br />
You might want to check in the bazaar and see if you can find a &quot;Tambourine of Rituals&quot;.  They were in good supply and relatively cheap (under 50 pp) on my server, and they are a much better drum than the store-bought ones.  (I don't care WHO you are.  With that in my hand your SoW only slows me down.  Thanks anyway.)
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
