				<td colspan="2"><span>fear kiting is scary at first, but just practice on some lower mobs until you have it all mastered. 
<br />

<br />
1. Fear in open areas so you don't hit friendly mobs
<br />

<br />
2. twist snare, fear, jonthans
<br />

<br />
Once you find a good spot to fear them along a path you will love it.
<br />

<br />
If you don't like it, then save up for some decent drums and start kiting!</span></td>
